{"tid":1136197,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"紀律部隊爭取加薪7%，呢個年代廢柴先打私工","createTime":"2019-05-03T00:12:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-03T04:10:47.000Z","uid":58669,"like":12,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"64e88c6bd7322875be265bcd5f19ebd37782ffcf","tid":1136197,"uid":58669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T00:12:53.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】公務員薪酬趨勢調查報告預計本月中公布。紀律部隊評議會、警務督察協會和警察員佐級協會召開特別會議，要求政府加薪不少於7%及6.5%。<br />\n<br />\n他們要求政府為紀律部隊成立獨立薪酬趨勢調查 ，除考慮薪酬指標以外，其他重要因素包括公務員士氣、生活費用、通脹、政府財政狀況等，並免除扣減每年遞增薪酬開支，紀律部隊評議會及警察職方分別要求政府加薪不少於百分之7及百分之6.5。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/紀律部隊爭取加薪7-093005749.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%E7%B4%80%E5%BE%8B%E9%83%A8%E9%9A%8A%E7%88%AD%E5%8F%96%E5%8A%A0%E8%96%AA7-093005749.html&d=YcIJTvf9PmU%2BR6jslv3gjFxDM7DnHmdvX2f5RcY9ddA%3D&h=5fccff6b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/紀律部隊爭取加薪7-093005749.html</a>"},{"pid":"d0dc2c09b44d2d75c56f509e66b3d3e9a53efda9","tid":1136197,"uid":120658,"like":17,"dislike":12,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T00:13:53.000Z","msg":"最廢果班加最多，公平？"},{"pid":"c4b50473263d41ad08fdb4f384f98513da3f50d8","tid":1136197,"uid":86756,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T00:35:44.000Z","msg":"做懲教最慘"},{"pid":"f0b47310526302103011d8adac86663b69cd9b22","tid":1136197,"uid":181418,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T00:38:14.000Z","msg":"要求姐，唔會比到咁高"},{"pid":"b178b685df1b4fceeba45e6b13e1cdf1195ea7e0","tid":1136197,"uid":34773,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T00:39:20.000Z","msg":"狗都加人工？ 賊都無個，企街？"},{"pid":"dc85af2b88288a14b9e7f07a53329fb4cf479119","tid":1136197,"uid":247923,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T00:57:08.000Z","msg":"做狗好過做人"},{"pid":"9b9d6fe67ead5b43b22f4aec47831facb5602857","tid":1136197,"uid":35420,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"